quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  43,34,"Men wa…óayno kadi e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, dame e dan…óe e nda…ó…óu…óe ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo fii no …ďe unura e fitina on see…óa-see…óa."
  43,35,"Men wa…óanayno …ďe kadi cu…óaari kaŇčŇče. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; nafa mun ko see…óa mo juutataa. Ko neema laakara on ka Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …óoftii…ďe Allah …ďen, …ďe wo…ó…óitii e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e Alqur'aana, haa o ronki taskagol nde, haray o leptirte wuurteede e setaneeru ndu o seertataa e mun, ko …ďeyda mo bewre."
  43,37,"∆äin awaseeji coowodaa…ói non e …ďen …óuunii…ďe Alqur'aana, ko sakkotoo…ói …ďe e diina Allah kan, haa …ďe ronka …óoftaade Mo, …ďe ha…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, hara hi…ďe sikka ko …ďe feewu…ďe e goonga, …ďe ronka tuubude e nden majjere ma…ď…ďe."
  43,38,"Haa si on …óuurninoo…óo jantoore Allah nden aroyii √Ďalnde Darngal, o yelora wiide: ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa, an oo coowodaa…óo, wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal fu…ónaange e hiirnaange wo…ó…óondiri ! Tawde a bonii coowodaa…óo !"
  43,39,"Allah daalana heefer…ďe …ďen nden √Ďalnde: …óum nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√Īiriino ko'e-mon sirku e geddi - wonnde on hawtoyte ka lepte. ∆Āe sirkan…óon …ďe, ronnditantaako on huunde e lepte …óen."
  43,40,"∆Āee ko faa…óu…ďe e nanugol goonga, wumi…óu…ďe e yi'ugol mo. Hara non ko an Nulaa…óo, woni ko waawata naninnde faa…óu…óo maa fewna bun…óo maa majju…óo laawol focciingol ngol?"
  43,41,"Si Men aru ∆īettitude ma ado Men leptude …ďe, haray doo ko Men yottoray…ďe e ma…ď…ďe, leptugol aduna e laakara."
  43,42,"Maa hara Men holle yoga e ko lepte …óe Men kammbirani …ďe …óen, haray doo ko Men gaynoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe ha…ótanaa dartagol Men e huunde."
  43,43,"An Nulaa…óo, jogito kon ko Joomi maa wahayini e maa…óa, golitiraa …óum. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol goonga, ngol jil…ďuya alah e mum."
  43,44,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare non, ko teddungal maa…óa an e yim…ďe maa. Arma nde lamndite…óon fii gom…óingol nde ngol, e rewgol peewal hende ngal, e noddugol e mayre ngol √Ďalnde Darngal."
  43,45,"An Nulaao, lamndii e …ďen …ďe Nulunoo ado maa, si tawii Men wa…óuno tanaa Allaahu On, rewetee…ói goo?"
  43,46,"Gom…óii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen …óen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu yim…ďe makko …ďen, o maakani …ďe: ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow."
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe woni e jalugol …óe jalkita."